---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Hyperlocality. Personal Cartographies — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Hyperlocality. Personal Cartographies</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">CasCaDas ArtSpace, Barcelona | 2025</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>The exhibition explores how artists ground themselves in an era of constant movement and remote work. Responding to an open call, artists shared their interpretations of hyperlocality, resulting in "a collection of diverse voices – personal, migratory, rooted and suspended."</p>
      <p>The works examine how participants "direct their gaze towards the close," documenting everyday connections, bodily movement, and personal geographies within Barcelona.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Curators:</strong> Fiona Fell, Michalina Sablik</p>
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Lena Laguna Diel, Ana Lucia Garcia Hoefken, Sejal Parekh, Pol Pinto, Carla Rebelo</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/hyperlocality/1.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
